Mindmap Project #01 : "Personality"
Well, it's mixed-up version about how to distinguish for about 14 different personality types from many sources through the web. It includes traditional philosophy from all around the world (China,Java,Ancient Greece&Rome,etc.),aura,tarot,and numerology. It's not about believing or something like that. It's just my personal pleasure to know more about what our ancestors had left for us. So, which one is your type ? ;D
